### 4. Performance Optimizations

```c
// Implement efficient rendering pipeline:

// 1. Layer caching system
typedef struct {
    uint32_t layer_id;
    Texture cached_texture;
    bool is_dirty;          // Needs re-render
    uint64_t last_modified;
} LayerCache;

// 2. Progressive rendering
// - Render low-res preview first
// - Progressively increase quality
// - Cancel in-progress renders on parameter change

// 3. Multi-threaded layer composition
// - Separate thread for each layer rendering
// - Parallel filter processing
// - Lock-free composition queue

// 4. GPU acceleration
// - OpenGL/Metal compute shaders for effects
// - Hardware-accelerated blur operations
// - Efficient texture management
```

---

### 5. SVG Import/Export Enhancements

```c
// Improve SVG handling in nxcrender:

// Parser improvements:
- Full support for SVG groups (<g>)
- Transform matrices (translate, rotate, scale, skew)
- Gradient definitions (linear, radial)
- Pattern fills
- Clipping paths and masks
- Text rendering (with font support)

// Layer preservation:
- Maintain layer hierarchy from imported SVG
- Preserve blend modes if specified
- Extract and apply existing filters
- Handle viewBox and coordinate systems correctly

// Export capabilities:
- Export composition as layered SVG
- Embed effect parameters as metadata
- Support for .nxi format with full fidelity
```

