## Technical Specifications

### Supported Input Formats
- SVG 1.1 (full spec)
- PNG (8-bit, 16-bit, with alpha)
- JPEG (optional, for photo layers)

### Output Format (.nxi)
```c
typedef struct {
    uint32_t magic;         // 'NXIC'
    uint16_t version;       // Format version
    uint16_t layer_count;
    
    // Embedded size variants
    IconSize sizes[7];      // 16, 32, 64, 128, 256, 512, 1024
    
    // Effect parameters (serialized)
    uint32_t effect_count;
    EffectData effects[];
    
    // Layer data
    LayerData layers[];
} NXIFormat;
```

### Performance Targets
- Real-time preview at 60 FPS (for up to 10 layers)
- Export time < 2 seconds for 1024px icon
- Memory usage < 500MB for typical project
- Startup time < 1 second

